<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="loneliness-n">loneliness <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ləʊnlinəs/    美 /'ləʊnlinəs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>孤单；寂寞</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The study surveyed 500 families and found the main psychological problem people suffered was tiredness, followed by loneliness and anxiety. 
这项研究对500个家庭进行了调查，发现人们承受的主要心理问题是疲劳，其次是孤独和焦虑。</p><footer>2007 上海春</footer></div></div>